Detailed Description

A word bigram phrase request.

Member Function Documentation

- (id) init

Initialize a new bigram phrase request.

All available bigrams will be returned.

- (id) initWithMaxResultCount: (NSInteger)  maxResultCount

Initialize a new bigram phrase definition request with the provided maximum result count.

All available bigrams up to the supplied result limit will be returned.

Parameters:
maxResultCountThe maximum number of definitions to return, or WNUnlimitedResultLength to return all available definitions.
